					<img src="/media_stat/images/template/wine/how_we_organize.gif" width="239" height="22" vspace="6"><br>
					Best Cellars classifies its wines based on their taste and style, rather than grape type or place of origin. Our selections are presented in eight distinct style categories to help you choose the right wine for any food, mood or occasion. To learn more about any one of these categories, please click any icon below:
